.SS nodex node certificates \fINAME\fR
List TLS certificates on a node.
.SS nodex node subscription \fINAME\fR
Show subscription status for a node.
.SS nodex node updates \fINAME\fR
List available package updates for a node.
.SS nodex vm list
List all virtual machines.
.SS nodex vm show \fIID\fR
Show details for a virtual machine (e.g., pve\-a/100).
.SS nodex vm config \fIID\fR
Show VM configuration.
.SS nodex vm snapshots \fIID\fR
List snapshots for a VM.
.SS nodex vm snapshot\-config \fIID\fR \fINAME\fR
Show snapshot configuration for a VM.
.SS nodex vm start \fIID\fR [\-\-yes]
Start a VM. Safety: Tier 1 (Reversible).
.SS nodex vm stop \fIID\fR [\-\-yes]
Stop a VM (force). Safety: Tier 1 (Reversible).
.SS nodex vm shutdown \fIID\fR [\-\-yes]
Graceful VM shutdown. Safety: Tier 1.
.SS nodex vm reset \fIID\fR [\-\-yes \-\-force]
Hard reset a VM. Safety: Tier 2 (Disruptive).
.SS nodex vm reboot \fIID\fR [\-\-yes \-\-force]
