.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Initialize configuration:
.PP
.RS
nodex init \-\-non\-interactive
.RE
.PP
Add a Proxmox profile:
.PP
.RS
nodex profile add lab
.RE
.PP
Set credentials:
.PP
.RS
nodex profile set\-credentials lab
.RE
.PP
Test connectivity:
.PP
.RS
nodex profile test lab
.RE
.PP
List nodes:
.PP
.RS
nodex node list
.RE
.PP
Start a VM:
.PP
.RS
nodex \-\-yes vm start pve\-a/100
.RE
.PP
Wait for a VM shutdown:
.PP
.RS
nodex \-\-yes \-\-wait vm shutdown pve\-a/100
.RE
.PP
Output as JSON:
.PP
.RS
nodex \-\-output json node list
.RE
.PP
Run across all profiles:
.PP
.RS
nodex \-\-all \-\-output json vm list
.RE
